Package ohos.event.commonevent

Class MatchingSkills

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.event.commonevent.MatchingSkills
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class MatchingSkills
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Encapsulates particular common events to which a subscriber wants to subscribe.

    MatchingSkills includes the following filters: event as an intent action standing for a common event, entity as a category, scheme as a filter for matching certain common events such as bundle installation and uninstallation, and IntentParams as extra parameters. You can use addEvent(java.lang.String), addEntity(java.lang.String), addScheme(java.lang.String), and setIntentParams(ohos.aafwk.content.IntentParams) to set these filters. MatchingSkills information is defined in the <skills></skills> tag of config.json.

    Matching Rules

    An Intent matches a MatchingSkills object only when the action and all entities defined in the Intent match the event and all entities in the MatchingSkills object.

    • Match of event -- Events match only if the action attribute of an Intent matches an event specified in the MatchingSkills object.

    • Match of entities -- Entities match only if all entity attributes of an Intent match all entities specified in the MatchingSkills object.
